description: This operation uploads a specific part of a read set. If you upload a new part using a previously used part number, the previously uploaded part will be overwritten.

parameters.name: sequenceStoreId
parameters.description: The Sequence Store ID used for the multipart upload.

parameters.name: uploadId
parameters.description: The ID for the initiated multipart upload.

parameters.name: partSource
parameters.description: The source file for an upload part.

parameters.name: partNumber
parameters.description: The number of the part being uploaded.

parameters.name: payload
parameters.description: The read set data to upload for a part.

nested_items.name: checksum
nested_items.description: An identifier used to confirm that parts are being added to the intended upload.
